cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.SD

The paper discusses a machine learning model (Mixture-of-Experts) and proposes a new algorithm for learning its parameters. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model is commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV) applications, which further supports these categories. The paper also mentions empirical validation on both synthetic and real datasets, which suggests a potential connection to statistical learning (cs.SD).
